    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Melee Tactics Toolbox pg. 19</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 10 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d4 (small), 1d6 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> B; <strong>Special</strong> disarm, see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Light; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Flails</p><h3>Description</h3><p>This odd weapon is a 2-foot rod topped with four blunt claws. Squeezing the handle causes the claws to close. You can use the gnome pincher to attempt a disarm or steal<sup>APG</sup> combat maneuver with a +2 bonus. You can transfer an object from the pincher to your free hand as a free action. Gnomes treat pinchers as martial weapons.</p>"
